{"tid":1979130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：斥美國歪曲《中英聯合聲明》","createTime":"2020-04-19T08:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T15:18:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":21,"dislike":214,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"108d50f4c61ed67352461f91e2c3cce48f93c50e","tid":1979130,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港公署反駁美國政客與香港亂港分子狼狽為奸<br />\n19.04.2020 15:48<br />\n<br />\n本港多名民主派人士被捕後，美國國務卿蓬佩奧批評北京持續採取不符合《中英聯合聲明》的行為。外交部駐港公署發言人批駁美國政客歪曲《中英聯合聲明》，拿所謂透明度、法治和高度自治作為幌子，為反中亂港分子開脫罪責，是助紂為虐、褻瀆法治，再次暴露他們與反中亂港分子狼狽為奸的醜惡行徑，必將受國際社會共同譴責。發言人說，香港警方對涉嫌組織及參與未經批准的集結的疑犯採取行動是依法執法，是維護香港法治，是特區政府在行使基本法授予的權力，合理合法，任何外國無權干預，敦促美政客遵守國際關係基本準則，立即停止干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281931&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281931%26csid%3D261_341&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=b3312ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281931&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"725c5bd4dcbdeef584b32b6b7c0632b23e84cceb","tid":1979130,"uid":172345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"煩撚到"},{"pid":"5ee6259f1a4ef49d926208015539441b08b22b3e","tid":1979130,"uid":264245,"like":130,"dislike":0,"score":130,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明原來係內政？英國是中國的？"},{"pid":"cc965d0ab36eaacc58d043aa7c68752253820462","tid":1979130,"uid":44358,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>等制裁啦，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4c86e1a4e1b1889c4d7fade8ed9ccecb965b6965","tid":1979130,"uid":31151,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意講基本法 基本法